{"tid":2387905,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"早產劉女士的「白警」言論","createTime":"2021-01-30T16:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T20:02:53.000Z","uid":326957,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a76925c1814d9cfe17bf672a6968954d34971e11","tid":2387905,"uid":326957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQkm9Er.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQkm9Er.png&h=e8715182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先澄清 我唔太熟悉劉女士嘅背景 <br />\n以下內容只討論「白警」言論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個記者係問「<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">如果小朋友大個想做警察呢？</span></span>」<br />\n個前設係佢個仔一定要做警察，劉女士答「<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">佢可以做白警</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於以上嘅回答，我地可以有兩個假設<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">1.劉女士唔相信白警存在，但因為問題嘅前設，佢被迫咁答<br />\n<br />\n2.劉女士相信白警存在</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">對於第1種可能</span><br />\n劉女士唔相信有「白警」。<br />\n我地可能得從劉女士嘅回答，推出佢討厭「黑警」。<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\"><br />\n面對記者嘅回答，佢一係間接表明佢討厭「黑警」嘅立場，一係佢推翻記者嘅前設。<br />\n而劉女士選擇咗前者。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n如果佢選擇以「我唔答假設性問題」、「我個仔一定唔會做警察」咁樣答記者唔算有禮貌，<br />\n當然佢可以選擇後者咁答，但其實無論佢點答，<span class=\"red\">都表明咗佢嘅立場</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">對於第2種可能</span><br />\n<br />\n劉女士仍然相信有「白警」。<br />\n然而，由藍轉黃唔係一步登天嘅天。要藍絲由「撐政府！唔怕」係短短一兩個月變到「連燈仔」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁黃係異想天開，痴人說夢話。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">我地唔相信「白警」存在，係因為我地見地好多警暴嘅行為。但藍絲所接收嘅資訊同我地唔同，要佢地係短時間相信「白警唔存在」係強人所難，由藍轉黃係需要時間。</span><br />\n用「做咗長時間黃絲」嘅角度去評論「啱啱由藍轉淺黃嘅同路人」係不合理。<br />\n我地要做嘅唔係「屌柒佢係藍絲」，「而家仲有人相信佢有白警？」，我地要做嘅係接納同引導佢地上正軌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬥黃係連登嘅風氣，亦都有好撚多5毛，但希望大家可以保持獨立思考嘅能力。<br />\n我相信個個人都有思考嘅能力，但呢種能力好易受到環境所影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五毛仆街啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純粹講下個人感受"},{"pid":"17a031de3bd2ef259ab9ff4ec3388deb84cab322","tid":2387905,"uid":248044,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"連衛兵算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c3f0d06e97f20a4a715c3b2e69d8dcbcd16d98","tid":2387905,"uid":326957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17a031de3bd2ef259ab9ff4ec3388deb84cab322","tid":2387905,"uid":248044,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"連衛兵算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"快撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7343d2cb07441f4a4dd10c8f8bdffa297dd6891","tid":2387905,"uid":110878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"算啦 訓啦"},{"pid":"30cf1a96834e5f4395d29add9e8e78ac4361b1cd","tid":2387905,"uid":248044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79c3f0d06e97f20a4a715c3b2e69d8dcbcd16d98","tid":2387905,"uid":326957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17a031de3bd2ef259ab9ff4ec3388deb84cab322","tid":2387905,"uid":248044,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"連衛兵算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"快撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"兒登已淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6793282d918441c38e6e679b2af3edd2819f5750","tid":2387905,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"求撚其啦 佢藍唔藍關我撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl